data.text:
Pearl & Jackpot Casanova Proudly Announce CKC Havanese Litter Ready 6/29

Coming home from a long day, Nina will be eagerly waiting to plant the sweetest puppy kisses on your face, while your frustration melts away! This munchkin is full of charm. She will grab the attention of all those around her! If you’re looking for a cuddle buddy, a friend or someone that will listen without complaint, Nina is it! This precious baby is just waiting for her forever family! Don’t miss out!

Born 05/06/19 Ready 06/29/19

See my Baby Book on Flickr and watch me grow!

SOLD: CONGRATULATIONS HUMPHREY FAMILY

Waiting on my new name and my new home is Jacksonville FL

What a cutie pie. She has been prayed over for finding her forever home .

I’m Nina I’m one of three females in this litter of five and I’m so sweet and loving! My litter theme names is from Spanish words to show off my Cuban Hertiage. I’m Nina that means Little Girl to show off my outgoing personality. I’m a gorgeous white color with cream markings on my face to highlight my baby doll face looks like I will have a light chocolate color nose too, so give us extra time on our outings as I will be a people stopper everywhere we go. My breed as a full tail and my will make you giggle as I wag it from excitement of seeing you, my hair is so soft his hair will entice you to run your fingers through it. I am hypo-allergenic and non-shedding so an extra plus for picking me. My mama Pearl is a 10 lb Havanese and dad Jackpot Casanova is a 10 lb Havanese. My birth weight was only 7.8 oz making my estimated adult weight is 8-10 lbs unlike regular Havanese that weigh 18-22 lbs Being born on May 6th I will be ready to join my new family on June 29th. Be careful because I’m ready to steal your heart!
